nodes.text: Rose Byrne (born July 24, 1979) played the handmaiden Dormé in Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones. She was discovered by Robin Gurland, the casting director for Attack of the Clones, while she was performing with Leeanna Walsman (Zam Wesell) in the play La Dispute for the Sydney Theatre Company.[source?]
